    <strong style="color: #e55039;">${startDate}</strong> to 
    <strong style="color: #e55039;">${endDate}</strong>.
  </p>

  ${weatherHtml}

  <h2 style="color: #1e3799; font-size: 22px; margin: 30px 0 10px;">üóìÔ∏è Itinerary Overview</h2>
  <div style="background-color: #f5f6fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #dcdde1; font-size: 16px; color: #2f3640; line-height: 1.6;">
